Domain   		           :  Banking / Financial Services
Problem Statement   :  Identify top-performing customers    based on total transaction value or balance.
	                     Segment customers((e.g., Loyal, Lost, New) based on transaction frequency, value, and recency.
                    	 Detect peak transaction periods   by day and time.
	                    Create interactive dashboards   in Power BI for stakeholders to filter and explore data (by date, 	amount, customer segment)

